OL,3,CHow broke is your council?
OL,5,FAny story about "bankrupt" councils is
OL,6,Fbound to start in Birmingham, the UK's
OL,7,Fsecond largest city, .
OL,9,FComplaining of a loss of #1bn funding
OL,10,Ffrom the government but accused of
OL,11,Fwasting millions, whatever the cause,
OL,12,Fthe choices the council faced to
OL,13,Fbalance their budget were stark.
OL,15,FEarlier this year, they announced
OL,16,F#300m in cuts and a 20% increase in
OL,17,Fcouncil tax. This may not sound like
OL,18,Fthe stuff of comedy but ITV's Tonight
OL,19,Fprogramme found looking for laughs in
OL,20,Fthe decline of his home city.
