OL,3,CHow broke is your council?
OL,5,FSpeaking from the Glee Club where he
OL,6,Fhas been hosting weekly comedy nights,
OL,7,Fhe said: "I have found it very easy to
OL,8,Fmake jokes about Birmingham being a
OL,9,Fdump.
OL,11,F"Audiences used to love that. And then
OL,12,Ffor about five minutes when the
OL,13,FCommonwealth Games started, everyone
OL,14,Fstopped laughing at that because we
OL,15,Fhad hope. And then we went bankrupt.
OL,16,FAnd now all that old material is
OL,17,Fcoming back into my set!"
