OL,3,CHow broke is your council?
OL,5,FOnce again he can turn his attention
OL,6,Fto the streetlights going out, the
OL,7,Frubbish piling up and the rise of the
OL,8,Frat as services get cut ` a story
OL,9,Frepeated across the country with
OL,10,Fnearly a fifth of local authorities
OL,11,Fsaying they fear going bust.
OL,13,FBut it's also a story of pain and loss
OL,14,Ffor many vulnerable adults and
OL,15,Fchildren hit hardest by cuts to social
OL,16,Fcare.
