OL,3,CHow broke is your council?
OL,5,FThe Tonight programme met 71-year-old
OL,6,FLydia Williams, mother to two adult
OL,7,Fdaughters with severe learning
OL,8,Fdifficulties whose care home in
OL,9,FCornwall is closing because the owners
OL,10,Fcan no longer afford the running costs
OL,11,Fon the money they get from the council.
OL,13,FWith her own health failing, she
OL,14,Fworries what will become of them: "My
OL,15,Fworst fear is if anything happens to
OL,16,Fme ` what will happen to them. Where
OL,17,Fwill they end up? "
