OL,3,CHow broke is your council?
OL,5,FThree hundred miles away, Jeff Gill
OL,6,Fshares these worries about his 92-year-
OL,7,Fold mother, Winnie who suffers from
OL,8,Fdementia and faces eviction from her
OL,9,Fcare home.
OL,11,FHe told Tonight: "The council, they
OL,12,Fwon't pay the higher fee that the home
OL,13,Fwants ` so she is just stuck in limbo
OL,14,Fat the moment."
OL,16,FAs a pensioner himself, Jeff is unable
OL,17,Fto afford the shortfall and fears what
OL,18,Fwill happen to his mother if she has
OL,19,Fto move home.
