OL,3,CHow broke is your council?
OL,5,FJosh Hawker from AbleCare Homes
OL,6,Fdescribes what's happening as a two-
OL,7,Ftier system where families who can't
OL,8,Fafford the top up fees "are at the
OL,9,Fmercy of what the council can afford
OL,10,Fwhich is increasingly quite scary".
OL,12,FMeanwhile, back in Birmingham, Tonight
OL,13,Fvisits a youth project to see what the
OL,14,F#2m cuts to youth services mean for
OL,15,Fthe next generation and finds that,
OL,16,Fwith the loss of 40 such projects over
OL,17,Fthe past 10 years, there are still
OL,18,Fgroups working hard to keep young
OL,19,Fpeople off the streets and beat rising
OL,20,Fknife crime.
